de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.common

  • Packages that use de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.common 
    Package Description
    de.opendiabetes.vault.exporter  
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.common
    Package containing the functions that all plugins have in common.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.crawlerimporter
    This package holds the extension point onto which the crawler importer plugins hook on.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter
    This package holds the extension point onto which the importer plugins hook on.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter.ODVExporter
    This package holds the ODVExporter plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter.odvdbjsonexporter
    This package contains the OdvDbJsonExporter plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter.plotterexporter

    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter.slicelayoutcsv
    This package contains the SliceLayoutCSVExporter plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter.sourcecode
    This package contains the SourceCodeExporter plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.exporter.vaultcsv
    This package contains the VaultCSVExporter plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.fileimporter
    This package holds the extension point onto which the file importer plugins hook on.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer
    This package holds the extension point onto which the importer plugins hook on.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.ODV
    This package includes the ODVImporter used to import files exported by the ODVExporter.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.googlecrawler
    This package holds this GoogleFitCrawlerImporter plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.googlefit
    This package holds the GoogleFitCSVImporter plugin and its specifically needed classes.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.libretext
    This package contains the LibreText importer plugin and its specifically needed classes.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.medtronic
    This package holds the MedtronicImporter plugin and its specifically needed classes.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.medtroniccrawler
    This package holds this Crawler plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.miband
    This class hold the Mi Band Notify importer plugin and associated files.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.mysugr
    This package holds the MySugrCsvImporter plugin and its specifically needed classes.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.odvdbjson
    This package contains the ODVDBJsonImporter plugin.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.importer.sony
    This class contains the SonySWR21 importer plugin and its specifically needed classes.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.interpreter
    This package holds the interpreter interface.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.interpreter.dateInterpreter
    This package holds the date interpreter.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.interpreter.diaryInterpreter
    This package holds the diary interpreter.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.interpreter.exerciseInterpreter
    This package holds the exercise interpreter.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.interpreter.pumpInterpreter
    This package holds the pump interpreter.
    de.opendiabetes.vault.plugin.management
    This package contains helper methods to manage the plugins.
